# Agent Working Rules

1. Read [`plan.md`](plan.md) first before proposing or implementing weekly-plan Lambda changes.
2. Keep implementation aligned with [`architecture.md`](architecture.md).
3. Preserve DynamoDB item key contracts (`PK`, `SK`) and 7-day log window behavior.
4. Treat S3 prompt key `prompts/create-weekly-plan-prompt.md` as primary source with repository fallback.
5. Keep model configurable through environment variables; do not hardcode provider model IDs.

